====Usage notes====
In its original sense, a '''shuttle''' goes back and forth between two places. The term is also used in a broader sense for short-haul transport that may be one-way or have multiple stops (including shared ride or loop), particularly for airport buses; compare loose usage of {{m|en|limousine}}.

